<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA38">
<l>amaikkum poḻutuṇṭē yārāyi ṉeñcē</l>
<l>yimaikkum poḻutu miṭaicci kumaittiṟaṅka</l>
<l>ḷēciyē yāyiṉu mīṉṟuḻāy māyaṉaiyē</l>
<l>pēciyē pōkkāy piḻai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is the time to do it, if we are who, heart,</l>
<l>the time to blink? Even if it is abusing [him] about the matters</l>
<l>of trouble with the shepherdess, just speaking about Māyaṉ</l>
<l>with the productive Tulsi drive away [your] faults.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
